Slugify any string using given trans_table

# Install

./script/plugin install git://github.com/kron4eg/to_slug.git
cp vendor/plugins/to_slug/trans_table.yml config/trans_table.yml

You can define your own trans table

#Usage

Use it like this

>> "привет".to_slug
=> "privet"

or this

>> "привет".slugify
=> "privet"

